      *------------------------------------------------------
      *  EDIT DATE
      *------------------------------------------------------
     C           #DATE     BEGSR
     C                     MOVEL$DATE     W1DATE
     C                     MOVELW1YY      W2YY
     C                     MOVELW1MM      W2MM
     C                     MOVELW1DD      W2DD
     C                     MOVELW2DATE    @DATE  10
